Package: ropenaq
Type: Package
Title: Accesses Air Quality Data from the Open Data Platform OpenAQ
Version: 0.2.7
Authors@R: c(person("MaÃ«lle", "Salmon", email = "maelle.salmon@yahoo.se", role = c("aut", "cre")),
